<template>
</template>

  <script>
  import axios from 'axios';
  export default {
    name: "AppUserProfile",
    data() {
    return {
      data: [],
      loading: true,
    };
  },

  methods: {
    async fetchData() {
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('/api/example'); // Call Laravel route
        this.data = response.data; // Assign response data to the `data` property
        console.log(response.data)
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error fetching data:', error);
      } finally {
        this.loading = false;
      }
    },
  },
  mounted() {
    this.fetchData();
  },
};
  </script>
